entity.name: Updates on the Covid-19 situation in the Philippines
entity.description: This page provides real-time updates on the Covid-19 situation from trusted and official sources.

text:
Palace spokesman Harry Roque congratulated the country for "beating" the University of the Philippines' prediction.

However, the country has yet so beat COVID-19 as infections continue to rise and thousands are still left jobless due to to the govt's measures against the virus. https://t.co/NsWdcVenne
